{"tid":87612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：自己並非普京無意再參選特首","createTime":"2017-01-20T03:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T18:14:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cbdba6f7a67d9540fb5f2cf94f862ad0e03197e","tid":87612,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"特首梁振英周三發表施政報告時被問到，能否承諾不會再參選特首，他僅稱未來只要香港和國家用得着，會在不同崗位中，「用自己最大努力為香港人做事」。他今出席港台英文節目時被問及同樣問題，終表態無意再參選特首，笑稱自己並非俄羅斯總統普京，又指樂見泛民主派陣營派人參選特首，認為即使有5至6人參選亦無問題。<br />\n<br />\n前政務司司長林鄭月娥及前財政司司長曾俊華近日分別宣佈參選，惟梁振英只對林鄭月娥發表正面評價，形容她負責任有擔當。他今稱要待所有參選人公布政綱後，才表態支持誰人，又指好政策才是特首最需要具備的條件。談到即使民主派參選亦難有勝算，梁振英批評這是因為有部份民主派人士拒絕遵從基本法，或表明拒絕接受中央任命。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在訪問中再次拒絕回應涉收受澳洲公司UGL5,000萬元一事。他指擔任特首4年來，旅行次數大減，又放棄了每晚游水的習慣，故有點期待離開官邸。"},{"pid":"1037bf886bda9b81e3ace21245869e8bc0f34263","tid":87612,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:25:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56197488&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56197488%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=fgFrnIcvcWuwYkN8wU6h4XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=4270ae58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170120%26guid%3D56197488%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=0e8e5ced\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170120&amp;guid=56197488&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"fa01d57ff2d5689cd4b7ff5e1ad94a846244764d","tid":87612,"uid":42872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:37:04.000Z","msg":"n 屆唔選"},{"pid":"88accf4fe1eee92d6f6aeef629625c0a67c2cef8","tid":87612,"uid":71073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"快通知普京有條懵鳩串佢"},{"pid":"a5d904044dbf94681467db3e65af0f73772f6f58","tid":87612,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:39:30.000Z","msg":"準備做政協副主席，晉升黨和國家領導人，副國級待遇，享有大內高手保護，特供食品，然後等退休完滿人生，仲做特首日日俾人鬧咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398397ca44a9ae1212f4606c0143a47060818bb6","tid":87612,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:41:15.000Z","msg":"你串鳩普京, 你係咪想聽日一支核彈爆鳩香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593d64074d23bd3aaa989696899b771c4364b5c2","tid":87612,"uid":8313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"人地普京咩料你咩料呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nKGB做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eef0c263fa84cf9e514c7402c640bcc9a9b8fdd","tid":87612,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"普京：you邊撚個？"},{"pid":"736a53bdc5593fb063704aa409b884ca01346969","tid":87612,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"垃圾自比普京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4af384ad8cb399834216b8a8e7770530c8b57e","tid":87612,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"一介畜牲竟妄想同普京相提並論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b685c3a1c8e8100f24e67191532b9598349d98","tid":87612,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"港獨之父想挑起中俄矛盾<br />\n一有機會就起義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac15f3f8455c2a668f39aa9f67f09bb57de66aa","tid":87612,"uid":5413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:54:24.000Z","msg":"琴日有聽光明頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.